(Game):....Omikron - The Nomad Soul
(Region):...USA/NTSC
(Date):....April 15, 2001

The  PAL version of this  game was released  in French, this is  the USA version for you  Dreamcast lovers. To get this game to fit on a burnable disc I needed  to rip out the intro and  downsample some audio, and  now you can play it on your Sega Dreamcast. Enjoy!        